Sorterator - Basic Collaborative Sorting Game
---------------------------------------------

Requires node.js available at http://nodejs.org and a Browser. Tested with version 0.3.2 of node and Firefox 3.6.

Installation:

 1. Install node.js
 2. Run "node server.js"
 3. Open http://localhost:8000


Results writing:

After every completed game a file with a name of the format YYYY-MM-DD-HH-MM.csv is written to the current directory. It lists every click on a line in the following format:

   timestamp;diff to previous timestamp;player name;number
